title: NEW HOUSE TOUR!!! - KA Daily
html: NEW HOUSE TOUR!!!
description: asdfghjkl I am so fkn excited to share this with yall!!!!!! I have been having SO much fun designing and decorating everything for my new house. At first it all seemed a little overwhelming, trying to figure out furniture and design for the house because I'm NOT a creative aesthetic person hahah but I ended up being obsessed with this process. The key word for this is PATIENCE. It's only been six weeks since we moved in, but at I started ordering and purchasing furniture a month prior to moving in. Furniture takes forever to come these days, and it was my first priority over art, so now that all the furniture is in, it's time to focus on that next. So, to reiterate!!! (because I know people will message me and tell me things Im missing, cough cough, carpets I KNOW)- I'm still not 100% there yet but I'm so excited with how it has turned out so far and cant wait to take you on a mini house/decor tour. All links below are things I purchased myself, none sponsored. I just wanted to share with you guys where I found everything and give you a way to quickly find it if you're looking for something similar! ALRIGHTY- enjoy!
